# SYSTEM::TIMERA

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Counts up. Every 1000 is 1 real-time second. Use SETTIMERA(int value) to set the timer (e.g.: SETTIMERA(0)).
